Package com.paiondata.aristotle.common.base

Class Result<T>

java.lang.Object
com.paiondata.aristotle.common.base.Result<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the data
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Result<T> extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a generic result object that encapsulates the outcome of an operation. It includes a status code, a message, and optional data.
